{% from "components/ellada-dematerialised-securities-system-view/macro.njk" import elladaDematerialisedSecuritiesSystemView %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<dl>
  <dt>Dematerialised Securities System</dt>
  <dd>{{ elladaDematerialisedSecuritiesSystemView({ value: "sample-value", label: "Dematerialised Securities System" }) }}</dd>
</dl>

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>10 digits linked to the investor's personal details (name, ID number, passport number, tax registration number) and managed by the Central Securities Depository of Greece.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Central_Securities_Depository">Dematerialised Securities System</a>.</p>
